<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>fiery words • hot words</xh5><p> <i>fiery words—</i>said of an ardent, passionate address, speech, etc.: Bert really inspired the crowd into action with his <u>fiery words</u> at the rally.</p><p> <i>hot words—</i>words spoken in anger; a heated argument: He accused Valenti of drinking on the job, and after some <u>hot words</u> he sent Valenti home.</p> </entry>
